%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20got%20married%20at%2025%20and%20took%20a%20personal%20loan%20of%20%2415%2C000%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20wedding.%20I%20don't%20regret%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Groom%20putting%20ring%20on%20bride's%20finger.%20Rings%20exchange.%20Happy%20couple%20celebrating%20wedding%20outdoors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66feaedd9e0c5c2eeeea5762%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20realizing%20how%20much%20weddings%20cost%2C%20the%20author%20and%20her%20partner%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20loan%20to%20pay%20for%20theirs.%3Cp%3EKenji%20Lau%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20high%20school%20sweethearts%20but%20we%20married%20when%20we%20were%2025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20finances%20weren't%20great%2C%20and%20we%20realized%20we%20couldn't%20pay%20for%20a%20wedding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20took%20a%20%2415%2C000%20loan%20for%20our%20wedding%20that%20took%20us%20five%20years%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20now-husband%2C%20Adam%2C%20and%20I%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-high-school-sweetheart-relationship-stereotypes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20school%20sweethearts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20although%20we%20got%20married%20young%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20both%2025%20%E2%80%94%20it%20didn't%20feel%20like%20we%20were%20getting%20married%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20our%20love%20for%20each%20other%20may%20not%20have%20been%20teenage%20love%2C%20our%20view%20on%20finances%20definitely%20was.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20our%20engagement%2C%20I%20was%20in%20graduate%20school%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20living%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-biden-debt-cancellation-education-department-relief-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Adam%20was%20in%20his%20first%20real%20job%2C%20making%20very%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20as%20modestly%20as%20you%20can%20in%20a%20big%20city%2C%20squeezing%20together%20in%20a%20498-square-foot%20apartment.%20The%20day%20Adam%20got%20down%20on%20one%20knee%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20we%20were%20thinking%20about%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faverage-wedding-cost-in-biggest-metro-areas-of-us-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20a%20wedding%20would%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dde67029-92ea-49e8-9239-9f2d6444372f%5C%22%3EWe%20decided%20to%20take%20out%20a%20loan%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20wedding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20were%20touring%20our%20fifth%20or%20sixth%20wedding%20venue%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20if%20we%20wanted%20a%20wedding%2C%20we%20would%20have%20to%20do%20it%20on%20our%20own.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20already%20had%20the%20vision%20in%20my%20head%3A%20tons%20of%20greenery%20(%24)%2C%20a%20top%20photographer%20(%24%24)%2C%20and%20an%20industrial%20all-inclusive%20venue%20with%20a%20per-person%20price%20(%24%24%24).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20shortcuts%20where%20we%20could%20%E2%80%94%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroke-wedding-etiquette-invited-b-list-guests-last-minute-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20the%20guest%20list%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20under%20100%20people%2C%20we%20nixed%20the%20highly%20acclaimed%20videographer%20for%20a%20college%20student%20with%20a%20nice%20video%20camera%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20friend%20marry%20us%20rather%20than%20hiring%20an%20officiant.%20But%20still%2C%20it%20wasn't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20lay%20in%20bed%20one%20night%2C%20stressing%20out%20over%20how%20we%20were%20going%20actually%20to%20pay%20for%20this%20lavish%20event%20we%20were%20planning%2C%20we%20made%20the%20hard%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouples-debt-funding-instagram-worthy-weddings-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20out%20a%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c421ea5c-5aef-44d0-b8ba-dd274877f7ec%5C%22%3EWe%20were%20able%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20fun%20parts%20of%20the%20wedding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20have%20been%20young%2C%20but%20we%20were%20still%20aware%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-loans%2F40000-personal-loan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20impact%20a%20large%20loan%20could%20have%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20something%20like%20a%20wedding.%20It%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20stress%2C%20but%20once%20the%20loan%20came%20in%2C%20we%20could%20focus%20on%20the%20fun%20parts%20of%20the%20wedding%20and%20not%20lose%20so%20much%20sleep%20over%20the%20money%20aspect.%20In%20the%20moment%2C%20it%20felt%20right%20and%20now%2C%20almost%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20we%20don't%20regret%20that%20late-night%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20wedding%20was%20everything%20we%20dreamed%20it%20would%20be.%20I%20still%20look%20back%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20change%20one%20thing.%20It%20was%20small%20and%20intimate%2C%20and%20the%20extra%20money%20we%20spent%20on%20things%20like%20our%20photographer%20meant%20we%20had%20memories%20to%20last%20us%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sit%20down%20and%20watch%20our%20video%20(the%20college%20student%20ended%20up%20doing%20a%20pretty%20decent%20job)%20with%20our%20two%20daughters%2C%20and%20we%20cry%20every%20time%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20because%20the%20wedding%20was%20beautiful%2C%20but%20because%20it%20was%20the%20start%20of%20our%20life%20together%20and%20a%20reminder%20that%20we%20can%20always%20figure%20things%20out%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20it%20seems%20in%20the%20moment.%20We%20don't%20watch%20the%20video%20back%20and%20think%20of%20all%20the%20money%20we%20spent%2C%20we%20watch%20it%20and%20think%20of%20how%20far%20we've%20come%20and%20how%20despite%20the%20struggle%2C%20we%20created%20something%20beautiful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286a1dfcf-faa1-42bc-9780-ac4099e71dc4%5C%22%3EFinances%20have%20been%20a%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20since%20we%20took%20that%20loan%20out%2C%20finances%20have%20been%20a%20struggle%20for%20us.%20Not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20wedding%20loan%2C%20but%20that%2C%20mixed%20with%20student%20loans%2C%20having%20kids%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20ever-changing%20economy%2C%20we%20have%20always%20had%20a%20monetary%20worry%20in%20the%20back%20of%20our%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20paid%20off%20that%20wedding%20loan%20(yes%2C%20it%20took%20the%20whole%20five%20years)%2C%20and%20we%20learned%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20kind%20of%20bind%20we%20get%20into%2C%20we%20will%20find%20our%20way%20out%20of%20it.%20Finances%20are%20a%20huge%20thing%20in%20a%20marriage%20and%20can%20even%20be%20the%20reason%20many%20people%20choose%20to%20divorce.%20We%20are%20aware%20that%20starting%20our%20marriage%20with%20financial%20woes%20may%20not%20have%20been%20the%20best%20choice%20or%20something%20others%20would%20choose%2C%20but%20it%20taught%20us%20a%20huge%20lesson%20that%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20money%20would%20never%20be%20something%20that%20would%20come%20between%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20though%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20taking%20out%20a%20loan%20for%20your%20wedding%20if%20you%20can%20avoid%20it.%20At%20almost%2035%2C%20we%20likely%20would%20have%20made%20different%20choices.%20But%20our%2025-year-old%20selves%20knew%20what%20we%20wanted%20for%20our%20big%20day%2C%20and%20we%20made%20it%20happen%20together%2C%20and%20that%20is%20something%20we%20will%20never%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-took-personal-loans-to-pay-for-their-wedding-2024-