20more%20valuable%20than%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20the%20world's%2011th%20richest%20person.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-blackwell-ai-market-value-costco-jensen-huang-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20And%20Harris%20Fight%20For%20Pennsylvania%20County%20Known%20For%20Picking%20Presidents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20command%20center%20for%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump's%20campaign%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20hotly%20contested%20counties%20in%20the%20most%20important%20election%20battleground%20state%20of%20Pennsylvania%20sits%20in%20a%20small%20room%20of%20a%20strip-mall%20office%20rented%20by%20Erie%20County's%20Republican%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20otherwise%20sleepy%20office%20comes%20to%20life%20a%20couple%20times%20a%20week%20when%20the%20two-person%20staff%20hosts%20the%20volunteer%20network%20the%20campaign%20calls%20Trump%20Force%2047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20miles%20away%20in%20a%20bustling%20office%20in%20downtown%20Erie%2C%20paid%20staff%20and%20volunteers%20on%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20campaign%20make%20phone%20calls%2C%20press%20new%20campaign%20buttons%20and%20organize%20watch%20parties%20and%20phone%20banking.%20A%20chalkboard%20keeps%20score%20of%20door-knocking%3A%2012%2C000%20households%20so%20far%20toward%20a%20goal%20of%2020%2C000%2C%20or%20nearly%20one%20of%20five%20in%20the%20county.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20four%20weeks%20before%20the%20November%205%20presidential%20election%2C%20the%20battle%20for%20Erie%20County%20-%20a%20historically%20must-win%20county%20in%20a%20must-win%20state%20-%20demonstrates%20the%20urgency%20of%20identifying%20and%20contacting%20individual%20voters%20in%20a%20campaign%20that%20remains%20stubbornly%20close%2C%20accor