nocking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20pretty%20bombarded%20with%20mail%2C%20phone%20calls%20and%20texts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Erin%20Miller%2C%2038%2C%20a%20bartender%20and%20mother%20of%20six%20who%20recently%20moved%20to%20the%20state%20from%20Colorado%20and%20has%20yet%20to%20vote%20locally%20in%20a%20presidential%20election%2C%20making%20her%20a%20prime%20target%20for%20the%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2019%20electoral%20votes%2C%20Pennsylvania%20is%20the%20biggest%20prize%20among%20the%20battleground%20states%20that%20will%20decide%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErie%20County%2C%20a%20blue-collar%20region%20with%20177%2C000%20registered%20voters%2C%20has%20voted%20with%20the%20winning%20presidential%20candidate%20for%20the%20last%20four%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20won%20Erie%20County%20in%202020%20by%20less%20than%201%2C500%20votes%2C%20or%201.03%20percentage%20points%2C%20an%20even%20closer%20margin%20than%20his%201.2%20percentage%20point%20win%20in%20Pennsylvania%20overall.%20In%202016%2C%20Trump%20won%20Erie%20County%20over%20Hillary%20Clinton%20by%20fewer%20than%202%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Harris%20campaign%20and%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20have%20three%20offices%20in%20Erie%20County%20and%20eight%20paid%20staff%20along%20with%20more%20than%20300%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20bellwether%20part%20of%20it.%20It's%20the%20mere%20fact%20that%20this%20particular%20city%2C%20in%20this%20particular%20state%2C%20could%20ultimately%20decide%20who's%20president%20and%20they%20know%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marie%20Troyer%2C%2060%2C%20a%20retired%20teacher%20who%20got%20a%20job%20on%20the%20campaign%20answering%20phones%20and%20managing%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBOOTS%20ON%20THE%20GROUND%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20ground%20game%20advantage%2C%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20has%20found%20it%20hard%20work%20to%20mobilize%20Black%20voters%20who%20make%20up%20about%2016%25%20of%20the%20city's%20population%2C%20especially%20Black%20men%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoward%20Pratchett%2C%2048%2C%20a%20barber%2C%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%20because%20he%20is%20more%20%26quot%3Bfactual%26quot%3B%20than%20Harris.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20care%20about%20LBGT%20rights.%20We%20don't%20care%20about%2C%20you%20know%2C%20abortion%20rights.%20We're%20not%20worried%20about%20that.%20They%20don't%20offer%20anything%20to%20the%20straight%20Black%20male%20voters%2C%26quot%3B%20Pratchett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonty%20Davis%2C%2051%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20local%20youth%20program%2C%20said%20he%20appreciates%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20efforts%20to%20lower%20costs%20and%20plans%20to%20vote%20for%20Harris.%20But%20he%20warned%20the%20energy%20among%20the%20Black%20community%20is%20not%20as%20high%20as%20it%20was%20with%20Presidents%20Barack%20Obama%20or%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20not%20that%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign's%20two%20paid%20staffers%20in%20Erie%20also%20oversee%20two%20other%20counties%2C%20according%20to%20Erie%20County%20Republican%20Chairman%20Tom%20Eddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign%20and%20local%20Republicans%20declined%20to%20say%20how%20many%20volunteers%20they%20have%20in%20the%20county%2C%20but%20local%20officials%20conceded%20they%20have%20fewer%20than%20the%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20other%20battleground%20states%2C%20the%20Trump%20camp%20is%20relying%20on%20deep-pocketed%20outside%20groups%20-%20like%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk's%20America%20PAC%20-%20and%20a%20much%20looser%20network%20of%20supporters%20and%20volunteers%20to%20mobilize%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202015%2C%20when%20Trump%20emerged%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20Republican%20politics%2C%20Republicans%20and%20outside%20groups%20have%20significantly%20narrowed%20the%20Democratic%20advantage%20in%20voting%20registrations%20in%20Erie%20and%20in%20Pennsylvania%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Democrats%20enjoyed%20a%20roughly%2033%2C000%20voter%20registration%20advantage%20in%20Erie%20County%2C%20but%20that%20has%20been%20whittled%20down%20to%2010%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20current%20county%20election%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatewide%2C%20Democrats%20have%20a%20roughly%20338%2C400%20voter%20registration%20advantage%20over%20Republicans%2C%20down%20from%20the%20commanding%20892%2C624%20advantage%20Democrats%20held%20in%202016%2C%20state%20voter%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Talerico%2C%20the%20county's%20Democratic%20chairman%2C%20conceded%20the%20Republican%20surge%20in%20registrations%20is%20unwelcome%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20certainly%20don't%20like%20to%20see%20those%20registration%20numbers%20converge%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20bad%20news.%20The%20good%20news%20is%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20still%20think%20we%20have%20an%20advantage%20with%20independents%20turning%20our%20way%2C%20and%20that's%20making%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20also%20are%20banking%20on%20Trump's%20frequent%20visits%20-%20five%20rallies%20over%20three%20campaigns%20in%20Erie%2C%20including%20two%20visits%20this%20election.%20The%20rallies%20represent%20mobilizing%20opportunities%20as%20organizers%20register%20voters%20and%20collect%20cell%20phone%20numbers%20and%20email%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20will%20make%20her%20first%20visit%20to%20Erie%20on%20October%2014.%20Her%20running%20mate%20Tim%20Walz%20visited%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there's%20Trump%20Force%2047%2C%20the%20volunteer%20network%20that%20knocks%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20infrequent%20voters%20to%20determine%20whether%20they%20plan%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20for%20whom.%20Volunteers%20win%20awards%2C%20such%20as%20hats%20and%20sweaters%2C%20for%20knocking%20on%20more%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20trying%20to%20persuade%20anyone.%20It's%20more%20just%20that%20the%20campaign%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20who%20are%20already%20inclined%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%20get%20out%20and%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20volunteer%20Justin%20Berkheimer%2C%2039%2C%20who%20works%20at%20a%20group%20home%20for%20people%20with%20mental%20disabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20HEATED%20CAMPAIGN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20both%20campaigns%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20fight%20for%20Erie%20has%20spilled%20over%20into%20threats%2C%20antagonism%20and%20uncomfortable%20conversations%2C%20volunteers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20half-dozen%20die-hard%20Trump%20fans%20told%20Reuters%20they%20are%20uncomfortable%20being%20seen%20as%20public%20supporters%20of%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20departure%20from%202016%20when%20Erie%20was%20flooded%20with%20Trump%20signs%2C%20according%20to%20local%20officials%20and%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Fuller%2C%2050%2C%20a%20credit%20union%20employee%20who%20said%20he%20has%20knocked%20on%20more%20than%202%2C000%20doors%20for%20Trump%20this%20election%2C%20said%20he%20leaves%20his%20red%20MAGA%20hat%20at%20home%20to%20avoid%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20afraid%20to%20get%20involved%2C%20because%20they%20are%20afraid%20that%20somebody%20will%20swear%20at%20them%20or%20threaten%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Fuller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20volunteers%20said%20they%20had%20their%20cars%20spit%20on%20for%20displaying%20Trump%20bumper%20stickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounty%20Democrats%20said%20they%20ran%20into%20tensions%20when%20they%20pushed%20into%20rural%20areas%2C%20opening%20up%20a%20satellite%20office%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20county%20that%20Trump%20won%20with%2072%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteer%20Kelly%20Chelton%2C