u%2C%20where%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20go%20toe-to-toe%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20also%20been%20abysmal.%20It%20has%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20and%20its%20few%20victories%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20seen%20as%20piggybacking%20on%20ally%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20undercut%20the%20Congress's%20newly%20minted%20ascendency%20and%20weaken%20its%20position%20within%20the%20Opposition.%C2%A0And%20the%20process%20has%20already%20started%20with%20a%20string%20of%20snubs%20from%20Maharashtra%20ally%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20%C2%A0Party%2C%20The%20latter%20has%20declined%20a%20seat-share%20request%20for%20by-polls%20to%2010%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20seats%20later%20this%20year.%20An%20editorial%20in%20Sena%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20spoke%20of%20the%20Congress's%20ability%20to%20%26quot%3Bturn%20a%20winning%20innings%20into%20a%20defeat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20score%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year%20-%2099%20seats%2C%20up%20from%2052%20in%202019%20--%20had%20earned%20it%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20giving%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20a%20voice%20and%20a%20new%20heft%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20this%20round%20of%20assembly%20polls%20have%20discredited%20exit%20polls%2C%20once%20again.%20The%20Congress%2C%20anticipating%20a%20big%20win%20in%20Haryana%2C%20ended%20up%20second%20with%2037%20seats%20-%20an%20outcome%20that%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20factionalism%20within%20its%20state%20unit%2C%20complacency%20after%20the%20improved%20performance%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20faulty%20strategy%20that%20placed%20all%20its%20eggs%20in%20the%20Jat%20basket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%2048%20seats%2C%20have%20said%20the%20over-emphasis%20on%20Jats%20has%20only%20polarised%20the%20state%2C%20with%20the%20non-Jat%20voters%20rallying%20behind%20the%20party.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20in%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20Congress%2C%20expected%20to%20retain%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20win%20back%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20left%20empty-handed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20a%20copycat%20situation%20of%20Haryana.%20Said%20to%20be%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20massive%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20government%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20it%20had%20delivered%20a%20massive%20mandate%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20left%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20shaky%20position%20in%20the%20Opposition%20block%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20had%20to%20curb%20its%20ambition%20and%20reinvent%20itself%20as%20a%20team%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20this%20phase%20of%20state%20elections%20can%20affect%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Kashmir%20party%20was%20expected%20be%20the%20dominant%20partner%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20given%20the%20Congress%20performance%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20talk%20on%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20concern%20that%20the%20outcome%20may%20leave%20the%20party%20in%20a%20weaker%20position%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20where%20talks%20are%20in%20progress%20over%20the%20knotty%20subject%20of%20seat%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saamna%20editorial%20has%20already%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20failing%20to%20accommodate%20alliance%20partners%20like%20the%20AAP%20or%20control%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisobedience%20of%20local%20leaders%26quot%3B.%20It%20even%20pointed%20out%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20last