2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Kapusta%2C%20a%20self-described%20%26quot%3BTesla%20fanboy%26quot%3B%20from%20Orlando%20who%20owns%20the%20top-of-the-line%20Cyberbeast%20variant%20of%20the%20truck%2C%20said%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20wait%20an%20unknown%20amount%20of%20time%20for%20his%20Cybertruck%20off-road%20light%20bar%20add-on%20to%20arrive%20after%20paying%20over%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Burtman%2C%20a%20Cybertruck%20owner%20from%20Harrisburg%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20received%20his%20vehicle%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20weeks%20and%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bincredible.%26quot%3B%20But%20he's%20still%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20get%20the%20FSD%20update%20without%20access%20to%20home%20WiFi%20from%20his%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJay%20O'Brien%2C%20a%20Cybertruck%20owner%20from%20Kansas%20City%2C%20Missouri%2C%20said%20the%20truck%20exceeded%20his%20expectations.%20But%20he's%20still%20waiting%20for%20his%20wall%20charger%20to%20be%20installed%20and%20new%20wheel%20covers%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20come%20a%20month%20after%20he%20got%20the%20car%20in%20May.%20He%20said%20the%20wheel%20covers%20don't%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20does%20matter%20is%20setting%20expectations%20to%20a%20consumer%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20delivering%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255339d69-93fe-4c31-ad06-a910836463d0%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20owners%20feel%20like%20celebrities%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you%20might%20get%20the%20finger%20while%20driving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20often%2C%20getting%20flipped%20off%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20right%20of%20passage%20of%20sorts%20for%20most%20Cybertruck%20owners.%20Some%20also%20reported%20getting%20cut%20off%20or%20cursed%20at%20by%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-owner-finger-injury-splint-frunk-teset-2024-5%