.com%2Fwhat-openai-needs-to-do-to-become-for-profit-altman-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20transition%20from%20a%20nonprofit%20%3C%2Fa%3Estructure%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcapped-profit%26quot%3B%20structure%20a%20%26quot%3Btextbook%20tale%20of%20altruism%20versus%20greed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20cofounded%20OpenAI%20as%20a%20nonprofit%20AI%20lab%20in%202015%20with%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-openai-cofounders-are-now-sam-altman-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enine%20others%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20later%20resigned%20from%20the%20company's%20board%20of%20directors%20in%202018%2C%20a%20year%20before%20the%20company%20announced%20its%20for-profit%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Musk's%20lawsuit%2C%20OpenAI%20called%20it%20the%20latest%20move%20in%20Musk's%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20blusterous%20campaign%20to%20harass%20OpenAI%20for%20his%20own%20competitive%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20safe%20and%20beneficial%20development%20of%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(%26quot%3BAGI%26quot%3B)%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI's%20lawyers%20said%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BMusk%20once%20supported%20OpenAI%20in%20that%20mission%20but%20abandoned%20the%20venture%20when%20his%20bid%20to%20dominate%20it%20failed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BSince%20launching%20a%20competing%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%2C%20xAI%2C%20Musk%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20leverage%20the%20judicial%20system%20for%20an%20edge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20asked%20for%20the%20case%20to%20be%20dismissed%2C%20arguing%20that%20Musk%20failed%20to%20offer%20factual%20or%20%26quot%3Blegal%20scaffolding%20needed%20to%20sustain%20his%20claims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Musk%20and%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20c