22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fdavid-tennant-cush-jumbo-macbeth-cinema-release-uk-us-clip-1236171166%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Shilpa%20Shetty%2C%20Husband%20Raj%20Kundra%20Challenge%20Eviction%20Notice%20In%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Shilpa%20Shetty%20and%20her%20businessman%20husband%20Raj%20Kundra%20have%20moved%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20challenging%20ED's%20notice%20directing%20them%20to%20vacate%20their%20house%20in%20Mumbai's%20Juhu%20area%20and%20a%20farmhouse%20in%20Pune%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money-laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pleas%20came%20up%20for%20hearing%20on%20Wednesday%20before%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Revati%20Mohite%20Dere%20and%20Prithviraj%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20petitions%20challenge%20ED%20notices%20dated%20September%2027%20issued%20to%20Ms%20Shetty%20and%20Mr%20Kundra%20directing%20them%20to%20evict%20their%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20a%20farmhouse%20in%20Pune%20within%20ten%20days%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money-laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20Bitcoin%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20advocate%20Prashant%20Patil%20said%20that%20Ms%20Shetty%20and%20Mr%20Kundra%20received%20the%20eviction%20notices%20only%20on%20October%203.%20He%20termed%20the%20notices%20arbitrary%20and%20illegal%20and%20sought%20them%20to%20be%20quashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20pleas%2C%20there%20is%20no%20grave%20urgency%20for%20the%20petitioners%20to%20vacate%20their%20premises%20and%20that%20the%20issuance%20of%20such%20eviction%20notices%20was%20uncalled%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioners%20are%20also%20seeking%20relief%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%20as%20the%20premise%20in%20question%20is%20their%20residential%20premise%20in%20which%20they%20have%20been%20staying%20with%20their%20family%20of%20six%20members%20for%20almost%20two%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitions%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pleas%20also%20sought%20HC%20to%20stay%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20eviction%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20pleas%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20in%202018%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20one%20Amit%20Bhardwaj%20and%20others%20for%20an%20alleged%20Bitcoin%20fraud%20and%20on%20charges%20of%20money%20laundering.%20Both%20Shetty%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20not%20been%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20during%20its%20probe%2C%20had%20summoned%20Mr%20Kundra%20for%20questioning%20on%20several%20occasions.%20Kundra%20had%20appeared%20before%20the%20agency%20after%20each%20summons%2C%20the%20pleas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202024%2C%20Ms%20Shetty%20and%20Mr%20Kundra%20received%20a%20notice%20based%20on%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20ED%20provisionally%20attaching%20their%20assets%20including%20their%20residential%20premise%20in%20Juhu%20that%20had%20been%20purchased%20by%20Kundra's%20father%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Ms%20Shetty%20and%20Mr%20Kundra%20submitted%20their%20response%20to%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20in%20contravention%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20law%2C%20the%20adjudicating%20authority%20confirmed%20the%20provisional%20attachment%20order%20on%20September%2018%2C%202024.%20This%20order%20clearly%20states%20that%20the%20attachment%20is%20confirmed%20only%20till%20the%20conclusion%20of%20trial%20and%20is%20subject%20to%20its%20outcome%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pleas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioners%20(Shetty%20and%20Kundra)%20on%20October%203%20received%20two%20notices%20dated%20September%2027%2C%202024%2C%20directing%20them%20to%20vacate%20their%20residential%20premises%20and%20t