0into%20transactions%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20loans%20too.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20where%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20rural%20lending%20startups%20comes%20into%20play.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20an%20opportunity%20knocked%20on%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20door%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20visit%20from%20one%20of%20SarvaGram%E2%80%99s%20staff%2C%20offering%20him%20a%20loan%20that%20would%20essentially%20take%20the%20business%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20by%20helping%20Ishwargowda%20purchase%20more%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECynical%20at%20first%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20a%20chance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20results%20are%20reflected%20in%20his%20earnings%20today.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20income%20from%20the%20shop%20is%20between%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20That%20isn%E2%80%99t%20all.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20loan%20lets%20me%20grow%20my%20business%2C%20keep%20more%20stocks%20in%20my%20shop%2C%20and%20sell%20more%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20one%20of%20the%20only%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshops%20in%20the%20Amargol%20area%2C%20the%20demand%20is%20always%20burgeoning%20and%20the%20loan%20is%20helping%20him%20meet%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20integrating%20UPI%20into%20his%20business%20operations%2C%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20kirana%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%