3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20this%20into%20perspective%2C%20Utpal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20mid-income%20households%20that%20may%20not%20necessarily%20have%20banking%20records%20or%20credit%20track%20records%20to%20prove%20their%20creditworthiness.%20Instead%2C%20their%20creditworthiness%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20%E2%80%98intent%20to%20repay%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20not%20data-dark%20households%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20ripples%20of%20SarvaGram%20are%20currently%20reaching%20over%2016%2C000%20villages%20across%20India%2C%20making%20it%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20tech%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20scale%20the%20dreams%20of%20households%20that%20once%20did%20not%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20formal%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishwargowda%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20his%20association%20with%20SarvaGram%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20few%20kilometres%20away%2C%20farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%E2%80%99s%20fate%20mirrors%20the%20same%20success.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20decade%20now%20since%20the%20farmer%20has%20been%20cultivating%20sugarcane.%20The%20land%20is%20cropping%20well%20%E2%80%94%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%20sweet%20drink%20that%20the%20farmer%20offers%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%20cultivates%20sugarcane%20while%20also%20collecting%20grains%20from%20neighbouring%20farmers%20and%20selling%20it%20to%20the%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%2