ight%20job%20(for%20the%20candidate)%2C%20and%20the%20right%20candidate%20(for%20the%20company)%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20job%20profiles%2C%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20project%20managers%2C%20designers%2C%20mobile-based%20application%20developers%2C%20web-based%20application%20developers%2C%20the%20front%20end%2C%20back%20end%2C%20full%20stack%20developers%2C%20testers%2C%20etc.%20We%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20state%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20that%20are%20hiring%20talent%20through%20the%20robust%20online%20community%20they%20have%20developed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EShework.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20offers%20a%20platform%20called%20%3Cem%3ETech%20Pundit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20connects%20mentors%20and%20mentees%20for%20personalised%20guidance%20and%20learning%20experiences.%20When%20we%20have%20tech%20mentors%20talking%20to%20women%20in%20our%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20community%2C%20we%20help%20them%20navigate%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20technology%20and%20what%20skills%20they%20currently%20lack.%20Through%20our%20community%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20them%20up-skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20regularly%20hearing%20catchphrases%20like%20%E2%80%98diversity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98diversity%20hiring%E2%80%99%20during%20recruitment%20drives%20by%20various%20companies%2C%20Pooja%20observes%20that%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20women%20equal%20pay%20despite%20having%20the%20requisite%20skill%20set.%20That%20is%20a%20major%20challenge%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20still%20have%20to%20convince%20companies%20to%20upgrade%20their%20salary%20packages%20for%20women.%20If%20companies%20offer%20a%20person%20a%20certain%20job%20profile%20because%20they%20are%20capable%2C%20they%20should%20also%20pay%20them%20accordingly.%20That%20is%20something%20which%20I%20feel%20is%20still%20lacking%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20hire%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20person%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Project%20Lead%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20so%20because%20they%20find%20their%20skill%20sets%20appropriate.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20they%20are%20not%20hiring%20talent%20because%20they%20want%20to%20fill%20up%20some%20diversity%20ratio.%20After%20all%2C%20that%20will%20affect%20productivity%20and%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20startup%20is%20a%20pioneer%20in%20India%20promoting%20women%20in%20tech%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Imge%3A%20%E2%80%9CStatistics%20largely%20show%20that%20women%20earn%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20less%20than%20men%