%E2%80%98Ecomark%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20product%20must%20possess%20a%20licence%20or%20a%20certificate%20of%20conformity%20to%20Indian%20Standards%2C%20as%20granted%20under%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standards%20Act%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECriteria%20for%20Granting%20Ecomark%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20product%20should%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20minimising%20or%20eliminating%20waste%20generation%20and%20environmental%20emissions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20should%20be%20recyclable%20or%20made%20from%20recycled%20materials%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20product%20must%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20non-renewable%20resources%2C%20including%20non-renewable%20energy%20sources%20and%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20should%20reduce%20the%20use%20of%20materials%20that%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%2C%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20production%20process%2C%20use%20of%20natural%20resources%2C%20environmental%20impact%2C%20waste%20emissions%2C%20product%20disposal%2C%20and%20packaging%20will%20also%20be%20considered.%20The%20notification%20outlines%20criteria%20for%2017%20categories%20of%20products%2C%20including%20paints%2C%20cosmetics%2C%20batteries%2C%20edible%20oils%2C%20tea%2C%20coffee%2C%20toilet%20soaps%2C%20and%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20clarity%20on%20what%20is%20the%20true%20scope%20of%20what%20is%20environmentally-friendly%20in%20terms%20of%20emissions%20and%20waste.%20Consumers%20want%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%